.Dd 21 December, 2025
.Dt VISUALINTELLIGENCED 8
.Os Darwin
.Sh NAME
.Nm visualintelligenced
.Nd visualintelligenced - VisualIntelligence
.Sh SYNOPSIS
    visualintelligenced takes no arguments, and users should not launch it manually.
.Sh DESCRIPTION
    visualintelligenced is the system daemon backing VisualIntelligence features.
.Sh HISTORY
    visualintelligenced first appeared in macOS 27.
